# app.py  —  Multi-Tenant Inventory Management System
# Stack   : Streamlit (frontend) + Supabase PostgreSQL (backend)
# Auth    : Supabase Auth (JWT-based) + RLS for data isolation
# Deploys : Streamlit Community Cloud (free tier)
